Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.71,0:00:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.18,0:00:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.72,0:00:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.83,0:00:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.04,0:00:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.84,0:00:54.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.12,0:01:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.56,0:01:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.23,0:01:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.87,0:01:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.57,0:01:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.52,0:01:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.55,0:01:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为这是乡间小路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.49,0:01:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.89,0:01:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个美丽的大自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我的心十分满足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.73,0:01:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，我已经不是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.67,0:01:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用那么关心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.14,0:01:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是罗姆斐拉财团所有的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.71,0:01:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉财团\N从前想以他的财力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保护这个美丽的大自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.41,0:02:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才赞同他的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.18,0:02:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在地球圈统一联合内部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,创立SMS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.29,0:02:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N那些拥有反叛翅膀的他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.79,0:02:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挡在我们面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.43,0:02:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十八话\N[交错的命运]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.62,0:02:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星派来的\N钢弹合金制机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.62,0:02:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那班优秀的驾驶员们前来挑战我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫五飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.58,0:03:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.06,0:03:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杀我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.44,0:03:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那种力量和勇气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.71,0:03:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们的每一次行动\N令我的心着迷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.44,0:03:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我不得不振奋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.15,0:03:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那方面你也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.58,0:03:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯‧马吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.12,0:03:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.75,0:03:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也应该为了目的单纯地战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.03,0:03:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把山克王国\N从联合手上解救出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.00,0:04:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士，全体出发了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我也出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请交由我掩护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.74,0:04:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你只想着达到目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.41,0:04:12.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已心无杂念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新型机动战士正急速接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.99,0:04:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有光线炮集中攻击那部机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.82,0:04:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我用了13年时间\N才再次踏上这片土地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你原谅我，父王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.69,0:05:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，很多人因此流尽鲜血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.20,0:05:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只能过着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.40,0:05:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,违背你完全和平主义的生活方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.40,0:05:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的手被血染得太污秽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.44,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样的我不能继承\N匹斯克拉福特王族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，她应该一定能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建立爸爸你理想中的国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.41,0:05:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会为了那目标而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.85,0:05:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请原谅我这个不肖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.66,0:05:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们站在历史的表面舞台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.49,0:05:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令时代向正确的方向前进了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的地方是宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.96,0:05:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安\N我把宇宙交给你处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.77,0:05:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向卫星的人宣扬我们的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.67,0:05:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果以友爱的态度和他们接触
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.14,0:05:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们也就会了解我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.31,0:05:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.32,0:05:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球圈统一联合崩溃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.65,0:06:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N宇宙有联合的残余势力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨伐他们，解放卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让卫星独立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.83,0:06:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是奉命处理宇宙的我的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.17,0:06:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人和我们的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.40,0:06:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和迪尔麦优侯爵的意见对立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.84,0:06:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而钢弹的驾驶员们就成为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.88,0:06:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个不断转变的历史的见证人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.95,0:06:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校!地球有通讯来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.42,0:06:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新加坡宇宙港基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.75,0:06:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正受到钢弹02和04的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上回去司令部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.43,0:06:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点!卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.77,0:06:49.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管我\N我决定了要掩护你们升空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋!你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.87,0:06:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家一定要去宇宙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，所以我在这里掩护大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少你们两个能去到宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.05,0:07:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下…剩下的武器…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.66,0:07:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有自爆装置呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.57,0:07:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…想叫我下去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙漠钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.42,0:07:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢你，你的沙漠钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，他们前往的宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.17,0:07:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有慰问和赞赏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有被当作叛乱份子的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.48,0:08:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤立和残酷的命运在等待他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.77,0:08:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的行动会受到很大的限制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,束缚会成为战败者...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.64,0:08:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一次力量的基础
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.58,0:08:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N现在的我反而觉得自由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.68,0:08:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许一直以来不大自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我采取的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.25,0:08:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为自己带来好的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你克服了我给你的考验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.60,0:08:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赢得自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.10,0:09:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯!别那么执着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.52,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，我不能成为你的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永别了，特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.57,0:09:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你离去后，罗姆斐拉财团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.07,0:09:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以兹巴洛夫技师长为中心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把感觉不到\N战斗的美丽和悲伤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.94,0:09:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.81,0:09:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们想用它们从宇宙支配地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.88,0:09:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寻求人与人的战斗意义的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.35,0:09:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能同意他们这种想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.69,0:09:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有你的OZ会容许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.29,0:10:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没用的人做出无益的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.51,0:10:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那达\N你果然厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.01,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙正逐渐认同OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.58,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.01,0:10:19.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校的表现好出色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.68,0:10:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她陆续和卫星建立起友好关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙建立国家的独立心态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会生产出防卫意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后以军事国家的身份站起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的各国感到威胁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.46,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会争先恐后寻求OZ的支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,了不起，特列斯，想不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.84,0:10:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把宇宙变为罗姆斐拉的一份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.47,0:10:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星是虚假的生活空间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虚假的和平主义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.21,0:10:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许只是\N产生更激烈战争的温床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.78,0:10:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯，不，米利亚尔特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你发觉到那一点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于宇宙卫星和OZ合并
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.69,0:11:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙的形势对地球影响很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.90,0:11:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我以一个国家的代表身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.53,0:11:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前来这里打听那方面的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.24,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个国家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘了自我介绍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.97,0:11:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是山克王国的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.91,0:11:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.44,0:11:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你从大人自小就有交情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.98,0:11:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,山克王国前来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.78,0:11:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听闻她在今次战乱中\N开始复兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道战争会带来什么的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.62,0:11:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能向想拥有武力的卫星好的建言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.03,0:11:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寻求和平有很多方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起学习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝着更好的方向前进吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.30,0:11:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你或许正在走一条明智的路呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安代表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.61,0:11:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心爱的蕾蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.51,0:11:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是正确的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个世上只要有人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.56,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争就绝对不会消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.56,0:12:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而否定战争不是步向和平之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.07,0:12:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界继续战斗是自然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.38,0:12:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.35,0:12:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯和钢弹的驾驶员们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.62,0:12:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在正创造未来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗的人有充实的感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.43,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而战斗的人不会堕落也是事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是任何东西也难以替代的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为豁出一切挑战敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战士的灵魂\N才会在满溢的悲伤里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.97,0:13:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高尚地在闪耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.31,0:13:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我一起落入地狱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天真纯朴的钢弹驾驶员们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直看着你们的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心底不得不发抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.66,0:13:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你们把内心的某种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.49,0:13:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至连我注定的命运也改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.13,0:13:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪吒，我们一定要强大起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愚蠢的罗姆斐拉财国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从战争中夺去人性的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我或许就被迫一定要亲手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.48,0:13:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把名为OZ的组织消灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.51,0:13:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，时代把命运托负给他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年轻人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.35,0:13:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们在黑暗里看见什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不断战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.54,0:14:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和推动时代的和平对抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.32,0:14:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人希望战斗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.36,0:14:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战斗是唯一的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.30,0:14:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不战斗就不能诞生任何东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.94,0:14:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯‧马吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.78,0:14:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，我永远的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.01,0:14:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚尔特‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.31,0:14:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ正在改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的力量已不足够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.79,0:14:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.02,0:14:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人类要走的路太任性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.12,0:14:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到扩张的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.49,0:15:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会把人类的心遣弃到这地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.33,0:15:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米利亚，有另一个了解我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.03,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是关怀我\N拥有两颗心灵的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.24,0:15:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你，替我救她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是为了实现理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.61,0:15:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了特列斯大人而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.56,0:15:30.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，我才没有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为在这场混乱的战斗里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.93,0:15:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只能走士兵之路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.30,0:15:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请带我去巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这时候，我开始发觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.68,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战争不只是实现理想的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.78,0:15:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人一定一直好想告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.26,0:16:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任务失败吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到你破坏不了基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.70,0:16:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又杀不了博士他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别那样说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…值得我来这里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.40,0:16:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高兴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.21,0:16:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和我的正在改良啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.28,0:16:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.05,0:16:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等着瞧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.35,0:16:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会再次变成死神啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.92,0:16:38.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使失去\N为宇宙卫星战斗的意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使自己被逮住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.43,0:16:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使失去心爱的机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.96,0:16:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那班钢弹驾驶员们也会继续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.90,0:16:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特尔?什么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.94,0:16:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要用这部钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.34,0:16:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把疯狂的宇宙的一切毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.38,0:17:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你告诉大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.55,0:17:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要在我面前出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我说过不要接近我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惊人的意志力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.01,0:17:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,惊人的纯真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我和他们固然是敌对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.48,0:17:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但大家寻求的战斗姿态\N没有什么不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.92,0:17:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦!快离开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.93,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜叶特要爆炸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.95,0:18:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.22,0:18:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来不得不承认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们是…\N这时代不再需要的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.34,0:18:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪尔麦优侯爵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我对罗姆斐拉财团要走的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢苟同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.18,0:18:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.48,0:18:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我认为人类须要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并非绝对的胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.02,0:18:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而是战斗的姿态和理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但使用MD般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.99,0:18:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无心的战斗兵器建立的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.69,0:18:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会成为被后世不耻的文化吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.33,0:18:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在他们充满纯真的感情前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.20,0:18:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传统会看不清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.27,0:19:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.77,0:19:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，你是说罗姆斐拉财团总部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.24,0:19:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从你手上没收OZ比较好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.44,0:19:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要把你软禁在罗姆斐拉财团总部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.45,0:19:17.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而我也下了决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.69,0:19:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要保佑和爱护
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.96,0:19:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能在战场继续闪耀的他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.59,0:19:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是不能理解的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.53,0:19:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你和我才成为敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.07,0:19:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要逃吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.54,0:19:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我先要报仇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.32,0:19:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我心爱的蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.99,0:20:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,安息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在遥远众星闪耀的彼方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.67,0:20:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,追溯至很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.51,0:20:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从我遥远的那心愿起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.81,0:20:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时间马上流逝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.12,0:20:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新星作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.22,0:20:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,罗姆斐拉团没理由会容许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.02,0:20:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仍然拥立我的士兵叛变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.26,0:20:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而他们为了\N取得地球上所有权力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.56,0:20:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把量产型MD-比尔哥降下地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.67,0:20:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在我没资格谈论这次行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.25,0:21:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对呢，希洛，去地球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.68,0:21:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然抛下钢弹离去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.95,0:21:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有什么打算呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，这部机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.26,0:21:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会创造今后的时代啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.23,0:21:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，为了第三幕的开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.13,0:21:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,演员正在集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.97,0:21:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之后只差等待揭幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.41,0:22:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.52,0:22:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切照特列斯大人的意思进行
